http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/%E2%80%98Submit-proposals-for-welfare-works-in-degree-colleges%E2%80%99/article14006859.ece

Collector D. Ronald Rose directed officials to submit proposals for construction of toilets and supply of drinking water in all government degree colleges.Presiding over a meeting held here on Monday, the Collector said that there are 18 government degree colleges and wanted the details to be submitted immediately. He wanted the lecturers to establish counselling centres in colleges and explain to the students the opportunities available in the market. He has also stressed the need of improving results and conducting job melas in colleges. -